Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,VANGUARD. AFCENT logistics in one sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,TMRs today take a week and three NCOs. VANGUARD does it in 60 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maps to the LOGCOM Transportation Movement Request Automation use\Ncase.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,200 assets, 50 bases across CENTCOM. No data movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Operator types one sentence — the agent fires real tool calls on a\NKamiwaza-deployed model.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,list_assets, compute_route, compare_options — streamed live in the\Nsidebar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Three options ranked. Recommended option pulses neon green on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL — same code, on-prem inference, 100% data\Ncontainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,VANGUARD. Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
